SUMMARY:Invasive Garden Pest & Disease Class
DESCRIPTION:Invasive Garden Pest & Disease Class \nMarch 11\, 9:00-11:00 AM \nThis class is for anyone who spends time outdoors and can help protect our gardens\, crops\, and forests. Join us for an update on current and emerging threats posed by non-native pests and diseases. \nFee:  $5 Members / $10 General Public \nRegistration required
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/invasive-garden-pest-disease-class/
CATEGORIES:Classes,Adults
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2025/12/spotted-lanternfly-4th-instar-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
